        <TextBlock HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="22,48,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" VerticalAlignment="Top" Height="324" Width="436" FontSize="18"><Run Text="Firstly, input your height in centimeters in the &quot;Height&quot; field."/><LineBreak/><Run Text=""/><LineBreak/><Run Text="After that, press the &quot;Begin Workout&quot; button, so that the treadmill can calculate your weight in kilos and display to you your body mass index."/><LineBreak/><Run/><LineBreak/><Run Text="Finally, you can press the &quot;Workout Plan&quot; button to have the machine suggest to you a workout plan personalized to your needs, or the &quot;Meal Plan&quot; button to display a suitable meal plan for you."/></TextBlock>
